model.items

Class Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.items.Item
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Item>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bicycle, FishingRod, Potion, SafariBall, XAttack, XDefense

    public abstract class Item
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Item>, java.io.Serializable
    This class is abstract because it serves as a parent to many child Item objects. Each concrete item has an associated image sprite.
    Author:
    Alan D., Paria K., Samantha F., Rajeev R., Scrum Master: Niven Francis, CSC 335 Final Project
